description: Louisiana Seafood Company is a food truck in Nashville. They are committed to fresh seafood for the local community! Louisiana Seafood company has a product range with everything from alligator meat to fresh crab. They have a great variety Gulf seafood; they specialize in boiled crawfish, crabs, and shrimp. Stop by to taste this delicious southern specialty! Their seafood is the freshest and friendliest in Nashville!
name: Louisiana Seafood Company
